{"tid":2408413,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"揸住7m預算，買御半山定帝濤灣好？","createTime":"2021-02-15T02:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T15:21:45.000Z","uid":46896,"like":15,"dislike":179,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"b30375837b2178095582315568ba8b29aea349ec","tid":2408413,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"首先，我有養車同埋喺九龍西返工，一直都住喺天水圍。唔預升值，想自住（住2個人）。想問下大家意見買邊度好？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w054XJh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw054XJh.jpg&h=2b2dcdd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTQAjWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTQAjWC.jpg&h=49dcbc88&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n兩個盤共通點<br />\n新鴻基樓<br />\n去最近嘅巴士站都要8-10分鐘步程<br />\n門口有小巴坐<br />\n御半山：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一手樓<br />\n行去景峰新墟有野食有野買<br />\n會所新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐巴士塞屯公<br />\npeak hour搭輕鐵去兆康要等幾班先上到<br />\n一層18個單位爭4部lift<br />\n難搵月租泊車位<br />\n<br />\n帝濤灣：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有村巴出荃灣，出荃灣一定快過御半山<br />\n車位比例接近1：1<br />\n一層4個單位有2部lift<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓下得一間百佳同7仔，冇餐廳<br />\n山卡啦<br />\n行去坐巴士係上屯公前尾站，要企<br />\n<br />\n御半山：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帝濤灣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e52259976f721beb4b849e7a5817ae6680cae8","tid":2408413,"uid":26071,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"7m買屯門區<br />\n一定係買瓏門<br />\n<br />\n養車方便嘅話可以揀深井碧提<br />\n青公沿線嗰d太偏僻"},{"pid":"2604b75985807df76585229b3f3013b33e7d8662","tid":2408413,"uid":46896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"79e52259976f721beb4b849e7a5817ae6680cae8","tid":2408413,"uid":26071,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"7m買屯門區<br />\n一定係買瓏門<br />\n<br />\n養車方便嘅話可以揀深井碧提<br />\n青公沿線嗰d太偏僻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:51:27.000Z","msg":"瓏門都正，西鐵上蓋，巴士行7分鐘去市中心搭又係vip區"},{"pid":"55f7284b9172554702741ede8741a01c10e0e55b","tid":2408413,"uid":13796,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"兩個唔同approach<br />\n如果塞屯公既話其實兩個分別不大， 因為易炒車既地方係汀九橋同青龍頭四線夾三線既位<br />\n<br />\n御半山由屋苑大門計行落去3分鐘唔使到景峰站， 有巴士輕鐵， 8 分鐘到紅橋有960, 唔想塞輕鐵既12分鐘到兆康西鐵站。<br />\n<br />\n帝濤灣唔計架荃灣村巴， 都好似要8分鐘左右先到青公巴士站， 如果你話行去轉車站仲遠<br />\n<br />\n計club house, 御半山嗰個好細， 雖然樣樣有，仲有架cafe 可以懶唔出街就咁落樓食都得。但成個紅橋你要黃店藍店粥粉面飯樣樣有， 24M記，24麵店都有。相反帝濤灣真係乜柒都冇， 仲要間7 仔唔係24<br />\n<br />\n但御半山唔係樣樣好， 帝濤灣拎住7球買到既size 一定比御半山大好多， 管理費平一截。仲要御半山質素唔係想像中咁好（地板垃圾，牆身油漆裂紋，仲要向山方向有墓， 向樓唔太開揚）帝濤灣如果向屯公方向除左食正西斜之外， 個景完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申， 買左御半山，住緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c78492771ec4fc5c81d0e4d9d0c18936a617539","tid":2408413,"uid":93958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔生仔又有車可以考慮下東涌"},{"pid":"28852a9cff750c086d06b49052bd829c4708e242","tid":2408413,"uid":89752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:22:58.000Z","msg":"東涌直屌九龍西"},{"pid":"5673e6108a66fb3382dd3bba147b9411e335b711","tid":2408413,"uid":360144,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"呢個價錢不如買四小龍仲好"},{"pid":"f0e0ba1a8ea545874f7dd8e85e9773fec3a68ff1","tid":2408413,"uid":46896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5673e6108a66fb3382dd3bba147b9411e335b711","tid":2408413,"uid":360144,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:00:20.000Z","msg":"呢個價錢不如買四小龍仲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"除左昇悅居一房外,7m唔夠買四小龍"},{"pid":"23028820a189315f8d3295fd0134f39bedeaa694","tid":2408413,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c78492771ec4fc5c81d0e4d9d0c18936a617539","tid":2408413,"uid":93958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔生仔又有車可以考慮下東涌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:28:37.000Z","msg":"映灣園長柒樓唔諗，東堤、海堤都可以諗諗嘅，昇薈東環就 14k一呎仲要駁車真係overpriced。"},{"pid":"ee1983bc4c27110589193045e159a74a7814a857","tid":2408413,"uid":116994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"有冇睇元朗？ yoho 1期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae711e13533cceb815d52a3b091cce8d7651fcef","tid":2408413,"uid":89761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:39:07.000Z","msg":"有車 就買深井海景<br />\n<br />\n麗城/碧提"},{"pid":"68b036c50092799c092e1ac97606a1f71b31e4ff","tid":2408413,"uid":354077,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>帝濤灣便唔係冇原因<br />\n大把方便過佢好多都係呢個價甚至便過佢<br />\n<br />\n況且帝濤灣向東向山太近就好似幅牆咁又多昆蟲<br />\n向西就西斜好勁<br />\n<br />\n小心日後放唔出蝕都無人要<br />\n你呢個價買參考同區大量競爭隨時蝕一球求售<br />\n<br />\n老老實實買番市區例如鑽石山啦<br />\n7m 400幾呎仲有選擇<br />\n日後有沙中線加上供應少蝕都好難蝕<br />\n放心鑽石山大把人有7m多到有D買居屋<br />\n所以就唔洗咁驚</strong>"},{"pid":"3b45b22640638c41b969f7ef57ab1fb568ff64eb","tid":2408413,"uid":391814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7aabf07c0225dfa15fb8471d0f0e97de86c6a53b","tid":2408413,"uid":391814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9befb0bd693ec440c397a990608c9834431df84d","tid":2408413,"uid":391814,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a91bf4352b9ebc2d67363a0c9524cb3b3386c8ad","tid":2408413,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06