"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:40:26.000Z","msg":"鑽石山邊個居屋抵買？利申 綠表"},{"pid":"aa6247a10143820c7164851ed37e11c573b6cb83","tid":2408413,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"移民仲好"},{"pid":"893397f58801da011efd7407907c108d51718b0e","tid":2408413,"uid":50099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9befb0bd693ec440c397a990608c9834431df84d","tid":2408413,"uid":391814,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b30375837b2178095582315568ba8b29aea349ec","tid":2408413,"uid":46896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"首先，我有養車同埋喺九龍西返工，一直都住喺天水圍。唔預升值，想自住（住2個人）。想問下大家意見買邊度好？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w054XJh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw054XJh.jpg&h=2b2dcdd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTQAjWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTQAjWC.jpg&h=49dcbc88&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n兩個盤共通點<br />\n新鴻基樓<br />\n去最近嘅巴士站都要8-10分鐘步程<br />\n門口有小巴坐<br />\n御半山：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一手樓<br />\n行去景峰新墟有野食有野買<br />\n會所新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n坐巴士塞屯公<br />\npeak hour搭輕鐵去兆康要等幾班先上到<br />\n一層18個單位爭4部lift<br />\n難搵月租泊車位<br />\n<br />\n帝濤灣：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有村巴出荃灣，出荃灣一定快過御半山<br />\n車位比例接近1：1<br />\n一層4個單位有2部lift<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓下得一間百佳同7仔，冇餐廳<br />\n山卡啦<br />\n行去坐巴士係上屯公前尾站，要企<br />\n<br />\n御半山：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帝濤灣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"700m<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hk